    <description>Distributes cancelation request cases to engagement specialists / account queue / related owner dependent on whether its premium target, non target, or enterprise (enterprise, gov payer, gov licensee). 
JH 4/23/24: small update to auto close all micro account cancel cases that get created from intercom
- JH Update 9/5/23: Updated to include logic to check if the account has a related payer account and stamp it on the case if so.
- 03/21/24 - PE - New Cancel Request cases should go to the account&apos;s SaaS Owner. If the user is not available, round-robin ownership.
- 05/22/24 - PE - If field Related Payer Customer Type = Government Payer, assign ownership to SaaS Owner
- 04/01/25 - BW - Updated to populate Opportunity on any cancel cases with a non-closed opp
- 06/06/25 - PE - Added path to assign ownership to EC Cancel Requests
-09/09/25 - DM - Added path to Auto close and cancel Intercom Small and Medium Permanent Closures
-10/13/25 -DM - Updated to account for cancel cases manually created in intercom as well as those created from workflow</description>
